The news_dir contains the sample news data used in training the language model. You could get it here:
http://www.statmt.org/wmt11/translation-task.html#download

To be more specific:
To dowload
wget http://www.statmt.org/wmt11/training-monolingual-news-commentary.tgz (From the News Commentary corpus)
wget http://www.statmt.org/wmt11/training-monolingual-news-2007.tgz(From the News Crawl corpus (2007 only))
wget http://www.statmt.org/wmt11/training-monolingual-news-2008.tgz(From the News Crawl corpus (2008 only))
To extract
tar zxvf training-monolingual-news-commentary.tgz
tar zxvf training-monolingual-news-2007.tgz
tar zxvf training-monolingual-news-2008.tgz

For this project purpose, the English news (file ends in .en) are kept.